    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, showing exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual gearbox and the factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle retains its original vacuum line routing and cooling system integrity, with no signs of thermal degradation typical of the platform. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing the signature 50/50 weight distribution and telepathic handling characteristics. This is a strictly stock, unmodified specimen with a clean undercarriage and zero structural oxidation\u2014a turn-key investment for the serious rotary enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Original paint with no blemishes. Interior is pristine. Full service records included. Mechanically perfect.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
