    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Every inch of the exterior gleams with a deep, mirror-like finish, completely free of swirl marks, door dings, or rock chips, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to a cabin that still carries that new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no wear, bolsters are firm, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, with every service performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the transmission shifts with seamless precision. Included are all original manuals, two keys, and a comprehensive folder of maintenance records. This vehicle looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
